Tue May  6 23:39:39 UTC 2025 - Guang Yee <gyee@suse.com>

- Version 3.2.0
  * Drops python3.8 support
  * Adds official python3.13 support
  * Fixes regex for colon output :
  * Fixes internal error with TraceLastReprEntry
